cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a new architecture for deep neural networks for domain adaptation in image classification tasks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves natural language processing techniques, which could place it in cs.CL (Computation and Language) as well. Finally, the use of kernel methods suggests a possible association with cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
